      <p>Looking to buy a contract phone but your bad credit score is standing in the way?</p>
      <p>Maybe you’ve contacted a UK network provider but they’ve refused to offer you a contract because your financial background makes them nervous. Perhaps they demanded a large deposit on a cutting-edge smartphone that you simply can’t afford to pay. </p>
      <p>Sadly, it’s not always easy to get your hands on the latest contract phones with bad credit. But at Mega Mobile Deals, we’re committed to changing all that.</p>
